.name
ChinaChallenge
.author
Dirk Hoffmann 
.version
II
.description
A game similar to Shanghai or Mahjong.  The goal is to remove all parts of
the pile, the so called Dragon, step by step.  This dragon is composed of
120 different game pieces.  You can always find four pieces displaying the
same picture or chinese symbols.  An update to the version on disk 312.
Changes include some bug fixes, unlimited undo, saving and loading of
games, background music, title screen, etc.  
